            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Even intranets require a minimum amount of security in the building.  Sales has confidential profit and loss numbers, while engineering has confidential intellectual property.  Many companies restrict data across departmental or divisional lines.&lt;/span&gt;

